{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HMAC","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/HMAC","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><abbr title=\"Hash-based message authentication code\">HMAC</abbr> は、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Cryptography\">暗号的</a>にメッセージを認証するために使用されるプロトコルです。</span> どのような種類の<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Cryptographic_hash_function\">暗号化関数</a>も使用でき、その強さは基礎となる関数（たとえば SHA1 または MD5）と選択された秘密鍵に依存します。このような組み合わせでは、HMAC-SHA1 などの複合名で HMAC 検証<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Algorithm\">アルゴリズム</a>が認識されます。</p>\n\n<p>HMAC は、完全性と認証の両方を保証するために使用されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"より詳しく知る","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia 上の <a title=\"HMAC\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/HMAC\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HMAC</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"technical_reference","title":"技術文書","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>\n  <p>IETF の <a href=\"https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2104.txt\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 2104</a> （英語）</p>\n </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"より詳しく知る","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"HMAC は、暗号的にメッセージを認証するために使用されるプロトコルです。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HMAC","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HMAC","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HMAC（密钥散列消息认证码）","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/hmac","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/hmac/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/HMAC